system, automated gearbox, anti-theft alarm system and a satellite
navigational system.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai Volkswagen was established by German Volkswagen and
the Shanghai Automotive Industry Corporation in 1985. The company
produces 250,000 Santana cars annually.
</P>
<P>
Hong said that the Shanghai Volkswagen is building a
technological development center and a special car testing ground
which will cost 1.2 billion yuan (about 145 million U.S. dollars).
