<P>
Macao's public security has drawn great attention from the
authorities and the entire society, and the government has spared
no effort to combat organized crimes. "The efforts to improve
public security have produced good effect," he said.
</P>
<P>
The veteran police officer said that gang members in Macao
usually do not target ordinary residents or tourists, and the
public security is not as formidable as described by some media.
</P>
<P>
"In fact, the crime rate of Macao is lower than that in some
large cities of the world," Cheong added. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
