<HEADLINE> Norway Extends Assistance to Nepal for Education </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An agreement to this effect was signed here Wednesday between
the governments of the two countries.
</P>
<P>
The Phase II Basic and Primary Education Program began to be
implemented from the current fiscal year starting from July, 1999,
with the aim of expanding access and improving primary school
enrollment of children, especially of girls and socially
disadvantaged children, in school or in alternate schooling
programs.
