Product Export Fair-99, aimed at boosting export of the
traditional industry, began here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The fair, which is organized by the Bangladesh Weaving Products
Manufacturers Business Association and will continue till January
7,2000, displays various products of weavers at 165 stalls.
</P>
<P>
