It will be Sharif's first visit to his hometown since the
dismissal of his government in a military coup on October 12.
</P>
<P>
Sharif, his brother Shehbaz and five others are facing charges
of criminal conspiracy, attempted murder and hijacking of a
commercial plane that was brining Pakistan's army chief General
Pervaiz Musharraf from Sri Lanka to Karachi on October 12.
